        "heading": "Sara's Birthday Event",
        "text": "<p>Forty and fabulous! Everyone’s invited to Sara’s birthday extravaganza!<\/p><p>Our queen of craft is celebrating a big birthday so we're going all out with an even bigger Crafter’s Companion party. <\/p><p>Join us for five days of fun, fizz, free gifts and so many treats! On April 23rd, the birthday girl is sharing the love on her big day. <\/p><p>It may be her birthday, but Sara has a crafty free gift for you when you spend £10 or more!* And, every day from the 22nd to the 26th of April there’s a brand new craft collection to unwrap. Each launch has been handpicked by Sara herself to make her birthday week even more special!<\/p><p>Treat yourself to something from any of the new collections to enjoy 25% off Sara’s books**, Craft Your Year or We Can All Make It. And end the week on a high by tuning in to Crafter’s TV on Friday, 26th April for a Sara Cartload special! You’re all on the guest list for Sara’s 40th birthday so head to the Crafter’s Companion website and join the party on Crafter’s TV!<\/p><p>*Free gift automatically added to online baskets with orders of £10 or more. One per customer. While stocks last. Offer valid on 23rd April 2024, ending at 11.59BST on that day.<\/p><p><strong>**Offer valid from 22nd April - 11.59pm BST 26th April 2024.<\/strong><\/p>",
